import React from 'react' import './about.css' const About = () => { return ( <>

About us

Rank boost is a guidance and counseling platform for jee students, here we guide students on how to study effectively for competitive exams and how to approach different subjects. we teach our students about what type of attitude and mentality they should have for competition. we teach all this through our rank boost guidance course. this course is made by the students who are studying at IIT/NIT. the content of this course is made by the thorough discussion done by the topper students. all the toppers have put their 3-4 years of experience in this course, and we have covered almost all the problems faced by the students while preparing for competitive exams.

in short, this is a booster course for your jee preparation, you can significantly increase your performance after watching this course, and hence your chances of selection in jee will increase significantly. we have personally guided many students and have observed that their performance improved a lot. we have seen students with depression and anxiety because no one is there to guide them and the platforms that are providing these guidance services are extremely high for a normal student to afford. so to solve this problem of students and take them out of depression and help in cracking jee, we introduced this rank boost platform

) } export default About
